cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on human motion tracking with a robot. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes to combine deep learning with model predictive control. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper deals with tracking human handwriting motion. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for online learning with a DyBM model. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper deals with control of a robotic system.
